导言 | 佛系氏言

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app80CX1DoD4392/a_5c66574e71cf1_KmhE03AY

<p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/2861300_1550210840.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="如来的掌心-04.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">唐诗宋词的美，张爱玲的小说，动漫中的人设文化，日本人的国宝戏剧……我们熟悉的日常中，一直潜藏着佛教哲学。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">最亲切的佛教文化，远不止《西游记》和《红楼梦》，在推理、怪谈、玄幻、影视、动漫里乐活和YY的你，其实仍然在如来的掌心里。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/23344200_1550210840.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="如来的掌心-06.jpg" class="loadingclass"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">16个佛系关键词，窥探佛教哲学的智慧，从经典文学、艺术、电影，以及流行文化现象谈起，开启一场活泼有趣又信息量满满的另类“佛普”。</span></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/43224500_1550210840.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="如来的掌心-01(1).jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(2